---

<section class="flex flex-col items-center text-center pt-16 pb-12">
  
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-10">
    <img 
    src="og-image.png" 
    alt="Logo The Creation Society" 
    class="w-6 h-auto mb-4" 
  />
    <h2 class="uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-xs font-medium text-creation-cream">
      The Creation Society
    </h2>
  </div>

  <p class="text-creation-gold text-[10px] md:text-xs mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest font-sans px-4">
    De idea a MVP con IA, No-Code y Low-Code.
  </p>

  <div class="relative max-w-2xl px-6">
    <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-2 w-6 h-6 bg-creation-gold/20 rounded-full blur-sm"></div>
    
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif leading-[1.15] text-creation-cream mb-8">
      Una membresía para founders que quieren construir, lanzar y aprender en comunidad.
    </h1>
  </div>

  <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-creation-cream/70 mb-12 max-w-md px-6 leading-relaxed">
    Únete a The Creation Society y empieza a crear productos reales junto a otros emprendedores.
  </p>

  <div class="relative inline-block">
    <div class="absolute -left-8 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 flex gap-1.5 opacity-60">
      <div class="w-[1.5px] h-7 bg-creation-gold rotate-[25deg]"></div>
      <div class="w-[1.5px] h-7 bg-creation-gold rotate-[25deg]"></div>
      <div class="w-[1.5px] h-7 bg-creation-gold rotate-[25deg]"></div>
    </div>

  <a 
  href="https://nahun020436.typeform.com/to/OMA0vJR8" 
  class="inline-block bg-creation-gold text-creation-dark px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:brightness-110 transition-all shadow-lg"
>
  Join the Waitlist
</a>
  </div>

  <p class="text-[10px] mt-6 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-creation-cream/50">
    Plazas limitadas
  </p>
</section>